             was indicted for <rs id="t18241202-50-off264" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18241202-50-off264" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18241202-50-off264" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18241202-50-cd265" type="crimeDate">24th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241202-50-off264 t18241202-50-cd265"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18241202-50-off266 t18241202-50-cd265"></join>, two pieces of rough Irish linen, value 2 l. 1 s. 5 d., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18241202-50-victim347" type="victimName">
                        Thomas Darke 
                        Allen
                     <interp inst="t18241202-50-victim347" type="surname" value="Allen"></interp>
